title: 03/21/22 DPS Hour 1 - Duke, Cleveland Browns

description:
In hour 1, the guys recap Round 1 of the NCAA Tournament and the moments we look back on that determine the success of a team. They also discuss the contract given to Deshaun Watson, which seemingly shows an act of desperation by the Cleveland Browns
